Yogavāsiṣṭha — Nirvāṇa Prakaraṇa — Sarga 186
सर्वं खल्विदं ब्रह्मेति
"All This is Indeed Brahman"
🕊️ The Journey at a Glance | यात्रा का संक्षिप्त चित्र
From the declaration of Kundadanta's liberation in Sarga 185, we now ascend into the pure teaching of Śuddha Brahman — the indivisible, attributeless Reality, where the distinction between seer and seen dissolves into the ocean of Consciousness.
